==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɔɪn|-ɔɪn]]

===Noun===
'''loin''' (''plural:'' [[loins]])

#<!--DefA-->the part of the [[body]] (of [[human]]s and [[quadruped]]s) each side of the [[backbone]] between the [[rib]]s and [[hip]]s
#<!--DefB-->any of several [[cut]]s of [[meat]] taken from this part of an [[animal]]

====Derived terms====
*[[loincloth]]
*[[sirloin]]
*[[tenderloin steak|tenderloin]]
*[[gird up one's loins]]

